name: Mors
text:
Death comes for us all. Renegade, runner, or royalty, every journey comes to an end.

While some Octavian cultists from the days of Mega City old believed Mors to be kind and fair, death was a feature of the chain, programmed in.

Of "eager teeth" and "skinless grin," Mors, second son of Somnus, comes for you, brave runner.
